directions: Combine the great Northern beans, salsa, pepperjack cheese, and chicken in a slow cooker.
Cook on Low until cheese is melted completely into the chili and the flavors have combined, 4 to 5 hours.
ingredients: 1/2 pound pepperjack cheese, cut into chunks
1 (8 ounce) can white meat chicken, shredded
title: White Chili VI
